WHY LINUX ?
Linux is an free and Open-source operating system with high security. Linux is multi user based OS.

Operating System:

An Operating System (OS) is a software that acts as an interface between computer hardware components and the user.

Every computer system must have at least one operating system to run other programs. Applications like Browsers, MS Offi ce, Notepad Games, etc., need some environment to run and perform its tasks.


